gory\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Bn nng cp\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/?p=1066\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:343:\"Phin bn WordPress 6.2 ra mt ngy 29.03.2023. y l phin bn quan trng th 2 ca d n CMS m ngun m WordPress trong nm 2023. Cc thay i c nhc n bao gm, ch yu  hon tt phn Chnh sa Block hon thin hn. Cc thay i khc Cc thay i quan [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Khoi Pro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5110:\"\n<p>Phin bn WordPress 6.2 ra mt ngy 29.03.2023. y l phin bn quan trng th 2 ca d n CMS m ngun m WordPress trong nm 2023.</p>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-1066\"></span>\n\n\n\n<p>Cc thay i c nhc n bao gm, ch yu  hon tt phn Chnh sa Block hon thin hn.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Trnh son tho ton b website bn chnh thc</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tm v chn Template  sa</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Thm code CSS trong giao din hoc tng Block</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chnh sa menu trong trnh son tho ton b website</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Lm ni bt khi ang chnh sa</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Xem cc kiu mu ca mt khi qua Style Book</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sao chp v paste style ca block</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Cho php chuyn Widget c sang Khi block</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chia tch cu hnh block v style block thnh hai tab ring</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Thm ch  Son tho tp trung</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ti u Pattern bng phn loi danh mc</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cc thay i khc</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Thm lin kt ti file media trong Th vin</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tch hp kho th vin nh cng ng min ph&nbsp;<strong>Openverse</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Thay icon mc Cu hnh trong son tho</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cc thay i quan trng dnh cho Lp trnh vin</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cho php khi nng cp/ci t gi plugin/giao din, mi th tin hnh nhanh hn.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2023/02/03/faster-updates-testing-complete/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gii thiu function mi&nbsp;<code>switch_to_user_locale()</code>.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/57123\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>To phin bn nhp ch khi ni dung c thay i.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/49532\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thm th tag cho cc phin bn style khc nhau.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/56869\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thm lc u vo d liu cho&nbsp;<code>wpdb::prepare()</code>.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2022/10/08/escaping-table-and-field-names-with-wpdbprepare-in-wordpress-6-1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>QUAN TRNG.</strong>&nbsp;Loi b function&nbsp;<code>get_page_by_title</code>().&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2023/03/06/get_page_by_title-deprecated/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bt caching cho function&nbsp;<code>wp_get_global_settings()</code>.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/57502\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check xem c th dng&nbsp;<code>mysql_connect()</code>&nbsp;hay&nbsp;<code>mysqli_connect()</code>.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/51988\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cp nht cc th vin h tr ln bn mi nht, bao gm:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>jQuery</li>\n\n\n\n<li>jQuery Migrate</li>\n\n\n\n<li>PHPMailer</li>\n\n\n\n<li>element-closest</li>\n\n\n\n<li>regenerator runtime</li>\n\n\n\n<li>polyfill-library</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Requests 2.0</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Ti u function&nbsp;<code>wp_kses_bad_protocol()</code>&nbsp; mang li kt qu function&nbsp;<code>esc_url()</code>&nbsp;nhanh hn.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/22951\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cho php tt&nbsp;<code>decoding</code>&nbsp;set&nbsp;<code>true</code>&nbsp;trong&nbsp;<code>$atts</code>&nbsp;ca function&nbsp;<code>wp_get_attachment_image()</code>.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/57086\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>H tr route regex cho tn template ting khng phi Latin trong REST API.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/57329\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thm action hook cho function<code>wp_set_password()</code>.<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/57436\" target=\"_blank\">Xem thm</a></p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>Bn c th xem bn y  bng ting Anh v nhng thay i trong WordPress 6.2<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2023/03/09/wordpress-6-2-field-guide/\" target=\"_blank\">ti y</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-extra-small-font-size\"><em>Ngun bn dch: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://codetot.vn/wordpress-62/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://codetot.vn/wordpress-62/\" target=\"_blank\">Code Tt</a></em></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedwe