(111, 1, '2025-05-12 04:02:32', '2025-05-12 04:02:32', '<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"hometext m-bottom\">Thng bo s 1 v nhim v: \"Tng kt hot ng nghin cu Khoa hc K thut o lng ton quc giai on 2020 - 2025\" (hay vi tn gi khc \"Hi ngh khoa hc k thut o lng ton quc ln th VIII\")<img src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/news/2025_03/ht-kh-ky-thuat-do-luong-toan-quoc-lan-thu-viii.jpg\" alt=\"HT KH k thut o lng ton quc ln th VIII\" />HT KH k thut o lng ton quc ln th VIII</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"news-bodyhtml\" class=\"bodytext margin-bottom-lg\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nThng bo s 1 v nhim v: \"Tng kt hot ng nghin cu Khoa hc K thut o lng ton quc giai on 2020 - 2025\" (hay vi tn gi khc \"Hi ngh khoa hc k thut o lng ton quc ln th VIII\"), chi tit trong file nh km.\r\n\r\ny l nhim v thng xuyn Vin o lng Vit Nam c giao c 5 nm li thc hin:\r\n<strong>Mc tiu:</strong>Tng kt, nh gi kt qu cc hot ng nghin cu, ng dng khoa hc k thut o lng phc v pht trin kinh t t nc, i sng, an ninh, quc phng v hi nhp kinh t quc t trong vng 5 nm (2020 - 2025); ng thi l din n  cc nh khoa hc v qun l ng gp  kin cho phng hng, nhim v pht trin hot ng o lng trong giai on cng nghip ha, hin i ha t nc v l hot ng thit thc nhm y mnh cng tc tuyn truyn v hot ng o lng ca  n \"Tng cng, i mi hot ng o lng h tr doanh nghip Vit Nam nng cao nng lc cnh tranh v hi nhp quc t giai on n nm 2025, nh hng n nm 2030\".\r\n\r\n<strong>i tng tham d:</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cn b khoa hc v qun l trong lnh vc o lng ti cc B, Ngnh, Trng i hc, Vin nghin cu, Doanh nghiptrong nc v quc t.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cn b lm cng tc o lng, hiu chun, kim nh phng tin o trong h thng c quan qun l Tiu chun o lngcht lng v cc B, Ngnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nghin cu sinh, sinh vin cc Trng i hc c lin quan v quan tm.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><strong>Yu cu i vi bo co khoa hc:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gi ton vn bo co khoa hc:<strong>Trc ngy 28/5/2025</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bo co trnh by (bng ting Vit hoc ting Anh), phng ch Time News Roman trn nh d