(127, 1, '2025-05-12 04:13:16', '2025-05-12 04:13:16', '<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"hometext m-bottom\">i thi SLEEP, mt trong 5 i xut sc nht lt vo vng Chung kt cuc thi Sng to tr 2024, s chnh thc tranh ti vi sn phm H thng nhng phn tng h tr chn on bnh v ng h hp trin khai trn FPGA\".</div>\r\n<figure class=\"article center\"><img src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/news/2024_12/hinh-anh-thanh-vien-doi-thi.jpg\" alt=\"Hnh nh i thi\" />\r\n<figcaption>Hnh nh i thi</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"news-bodyhtml\" class=\"bodytext margin-bottom-lg\">\r\n<div><em><strong>Ngy 28/12 ti y, i thi SLEEP, mt trong 5 i xut sc nht lt vo vng Chung kt cuc thi Sng to tr 2024, s chnh thc tranh ti vi sn phm H thng nhng phn tng h tr chn on bnh v ng h hp trin khai trn FPGA\".</strong></em>\r\n\r\nNhm SLEEP gm 4 n sinh vin ngnh K thut in t Vin thng, Trng in - in t, i hc Bch khoa H Ni: Nguyn Anh Phng - K65, V Th Ngc Trm  K66, o Cao Ngc Ly  K66, Mc Phng Nga  K66. Nhm nghin cu nhn c s hng dn ca PGS. Hn Trng Thanh - Ph Vin Trng Vin Nghin cu Cng ngh khng gian v di nc, i hc Bch khoa H Ni.\r\n\r\n<strong>Gii php n gin, khng xm ln, tit kim</strong>\r\n\r\nTheo T chc Y t Th gii (WHO), cc bnh l v ng h hp l nguyn nhn t vong ng th ba trn ton cu, vi 75% s ca t vong xut pht t vic chn on mun. Sau i dch COVID-19, tnh trng ny cng tr nn nghim trng hn.\r\n\r\nNhiu ngi thng ch quan khi gp cc triu chng nh ho hay kh th. Vi tm l e ngi, mi ngi thng chn cch t mua thuc thay v n bnh vin  kim tra. iu ny khin cc bnh l ng l c th c pht hin v cha tr sm nh vim ph qun, vim phi hay COPD (Bnh phi tc nghn mn tnh) tr nn nghim trng. - Ngc Trm chia s.\r\n\r\nChng em mun mang n mt gii php n gin, khng xm ln v tit kim  gip pht hin sm cc bnh l ny.  Nhm chia s v  tng.\r\nTrc khi bt tay vo pht trin sn phm, di s hng dn ca PGS. Hn Trng Thanh, nhm  phn tch u nhc im ca cc phng php chn on bnh l v ng h hp hin ti trn th trng.\r\n\r\nCc phng php nh o lu lng nh, ph dung k v chp X-quang l nhng tiu chun ph bin nhng u c nhc im chung: Cn s gim st ca i ng y t v cc mi trng chuyn bit. Sn phm ca nhm SLEEP hng n khc phc nhng hn ch ny, mang li s tin li v an ton hn cho ngi s dng.\r\n\r\n<strong>Phn loi bnh bng m hnh tr tu nhn to Random Forest</strong>\r\n\r\nSn phm ca SLEEP s dng m hnh tr tu nhn to Random Forest  phn loi bnh. y l m hnh hc my ni bt vi kh nng x l d liu phc tp v a ra kt qu chnh xc cao. Chng em tin rng y l hng i ng n, bt kp xu hng pht trin cng ngh khi cc m hnh AI ngy cng ph bin trong lnh vc y t, Anh Phng cho bit.</div>\r\n<figure>\r\n<div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://hust.edu.vn/uploads/sys/news/2024_12/hinh-anh-san-pham_1.jpg\" alt=\"hinh anh san pham\" width=\"1529\" height=\"1353\" /><figcaption>Sn phm H thng nhng phn tng h tr chn on bnh v ng h hp trin khai trn FPGA\"</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<div> gii quyt bi ton chi ph v tiu hao nng lng, nhm  s dng FPGA (Field-Programmable Gate Array) thay v CPU hoc GPU. FPGA khng ch gip gim thiu chi ph sn phm m cn tit kim nng lng ng k, p ng nhu cu s dng lin tc trong mi trng thc t.\r\n\r\nBn cnh , nhm cng ti u ha h thng  sn phm t  chnh xc cao hn so vi cc phng php truyn thng. Thit b hon ton t ng, khng gy kh chu hay xm ln cho ngi dng, to ra mt tri nghim thn thin hn.\r\n\r\n<strong>C vp vng bn kt</strong>\r\n\r\nMt trong nhng yu t quan trng gip SLEEP t c thnh cng nh hin ti chnh l tinh thn on kt v s h tr ln nhau gia cc thnh vin. Chng em u l n, hc cng ngnh nn rt d chia s kh khn vi nhau. T nhng bui ln lab n nhng ln i c ph tho lun cng vic, chng em nh  tr thnh ch em trong mt nh. Ngc Ly chia s.\r\n\r\nD vy, vic tt c thnh vin u xut thn t ngnh k thut cng mang li khng t kh khn khi c nhm u xa l vi cc m hnh kinh doanh.\r\nTi vng bn kt, khi Ban gim kho t cu hi v gi thnh ng nghe in t  mt phn ct li ca d n, do chun b thiu thng tin, nhm  a ra cu tr li cha chnh xc.</div>\r\n</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://hust.edu.vn/uploads/sys/news/2024_12/nhom-thuyet-trinh-va-tra-loi-cau-hoi-tu-hoi-dong-ban-giam-khao.jpg\" alt=\"nhom thuyet trinh va tra loi cau hoi tu hoi ong ban giam khao\" width=\"1900\" height=\"1083\" /><figcaption>i din nhm trnh by  ti ti Bn kt Cuc thi Sng to tr</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</figcaption></figure>\r\n<div>S c ny khin c nhm nhn ra tm quan trng ca vic chun b k lng v trau di thm kin thc, c bit trong lnh vc kinh doanh. \"Chng em hiu rng, khng ch cn nm r phn k thut m cn phi b sung kin thc a lnh vc  t tin hn trong nhng vng thi ti\"  Cao Ly chia s.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slogan  ngha: Cng ngh thng minh  Sc khe bn vng</strong>\r\n\r\nT nhng vng u ca cuc thi Sng to tr n nay, sn phm ca nhm  tri qua nhiu ci tin ng k. Thch thc ln nht m nhm phi i mt chnh l xy dng b d liu  ln v cht lng  nng cao  chnh xc trong vic chn on, c bit khi phn bit cc bnh c triu chng tng t.\r\n\r\nNhm cng gp kh khn trong vic thu thp d liu m thanh phi t chun, pht trin m hnh AI m bo  chnh xc cao v duy tr thit b hot ng n nh trong iu kin ti nguyn hn ch. \"Nhiu lc tng nh sp ngun, nhng ch em li ng vin ln nhau tip tc c gng.\" Cao Ly chia s.\r\n\r\nKhng dng li  sn phm hin ti, nhm SLEEP ang pht trin thm mt phin bn nh gn, tin li hn, ph hp vi cc h gia nh c ngi gi hoc tr em c tin s mc bnh h hp. Phin bn ny ha hn s c mc gi hp l hn, thao tc n gin hn, gip ngi dng d dng tip cn v s dng.</div>\r\n<figure>\r\n<div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://hust.edu.vn/uploads/sys/news/2024_12/hinh-anh-san-pham-phien-ban-nho-gon-hon.jpg\" alt=\"Hinh anh san pham phien ban nho gon hon\" width=\"1276\" height=\"956\" /><figcaption>Phin bn sn phm nh gn nhm ang pht trin</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</figcaption></figure>\r\n<div>Chng em mun sn phm ca mnh khng ch dng li  cc phng khm m cn c mt trong tng gia nh, gp phn thay i cch mi ngi chm sc sc khe, Mc Phng Nga chia s.\r\n\r\nVi slogan Cng ngh thng minh  Sc khe bn vng, SLEEP khng ch hng n vic to ra mt thit b y t tin ch m cn gi gm kht vng mang li gi tr lu di cho cng ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive table-responsive-all\">\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>D kin trong qu 1 n qu 3 nm 2026, phin bn sn phm u tin s c ra mt trn th trng vi mc gi khong 15 triu ng mi sn phm ph hp cho cc phng khm chuyn khoa, thp hn ng k so vi cc thit b nh my chp X-quang tch hp AI hay phn mm chn on COVID-19 qua ting ho. Trong tng lai, nhm s tip tc pht trin v cho ra mt cc phin bn cho h gia nh.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Chung kt Sng to tr 2024: T c nng Bch khoa v sn phm pht hin sm bnh l h hp', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chung-ket-sang-tao-tre-2024-tu-co-nuong-bach-khoa-va-san-pham-phat-hien-som-benh-ly-ho-hap', '', '', '2025-05-12 04:13:16', '2025-05-12 04:13:16', '', 0, 'http://web-hust.test/?post_type=tin&#038;p=127', 0, 'tin', '', 0),
