ng mang li gi tr lu di cho cng ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive table-responsive-all\">\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>D kin trong qu 1 n qu 3 nm 2026, phin bn sn phm u tin s c ra mt trn th trng vi mc gi khong 15 triu ng mi sn phm ph hp cho cc phng khm chuyn khoa, thp hn ng k so vi cc thit b nh my chp X-quang tch hp AI hay phn mm chn on COVID-19 qua ting ho. Trong tng lai, nhm s tip tc pht trin v cho ra mt cc phin bn cho h gia nh.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Chung kt Sng to tr 2024: T c nng Bch khoa v sn phm pht hin sm bnh l h hp', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-12 04:13:16', '2025-05-12 04:13:16', '', 127, 'http://web-hust.test/?p=129', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
