ngi dng) vng chc  m bo kh nng t o to nng cao trnh  chuyn mn.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">M hnh ha v phng to h thng truyn thng s v x l d liu a phng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Thit k m hnh truyn thng s v a phng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Thit k v pht trin h thng x l v sng to ni dung s a phng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">S dng thnh tho mt s cng c nn tng trong lnh vc truyn thng s v k thut a phng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">S dng thnh tho mt s ngn ng lp trnh c bn v nng cao</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">S dng ngoi ng trong giao tip x hi v thc hnh chuyn mn (IELTS 5.5 hoc tng ng)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Th hin k nng qun tr, qun l v hc tp sut i</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Thnh tho k nng trnh by, vit bo co</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Th hin k nng lm vic c lp v lm vic nhm</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Th hin t duy phn bin v sng to ni dung s</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Tun th php lut v tn trng quy tc ngh nghip</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl71\" colspan=\"2\">NI DUNG &amp; L TRNH O TO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl72\" colspan=\"2\">Chng trnh o to Truyn thng s v k thut a phng tin bao gm cc khi kin thc chnh:</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Khi kin thc i cngbao gm cc mn khoa hc t nhin v x hi c bn (Ton hc, Vt l, L lun chnh tr)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Thu thp v truyn thng d liu s PT(H iu hnh, Vi x l, Kin trc my tnh , in t s, Thng tin s, Mng my tnh, K thut truyn hnh, Internet th h mi, in ton m my/bin)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Qun l v x l d liu s PT(C s d liu, Cu trc d liu &amp; gii thut, Phn tch v trc quan ho d liu; X l tn hiu s, Nn v m ho d liu, X l tn hiu m thanh, X l nh, X l ngn ng t nhin)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Phn tch hiu ni dung s PT s dng AI(Hc my c bn, Hc my nng cao, Th gic my tnh, Nhn dng v tng hp ting ni)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Sn xut ni dung v trin khai d n PT( ho my tnh, Lp trnh game, Lp trnh web v di ng, K xo in nh, Sn xut ni dung s a phng tin, , Lp trnh C/C++, Lp trnh nng cao, Phn tch thit k h thng, Tng tc ngi my, Qun l d n)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/dao-tao/2024_09/et-e16cac-linh-vuc.jpg\" alt=\"ET E16 Cac linh vuc\" width=\"967\" height=\"822\" /><figcaption>ET-E16</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>', 'ET-E16-Truyn thng s v K thut a phng tin', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '184-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-13 02:38:38', '2025-05-13 02:38:38', '', 184, 'http://web-hust.test/?p=186', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
