(188, 1, '2025-05-13 02:39:11', '2025-05-13 02:39:11', '<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n<figure class=\"article center\"><img src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/dao-tao/2024_09/ettn-ctdt.jpg\" alt=\"ET TN CTT\" /><figcaption>ET TN CTT</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"news-bodyhtml\" class=\"bodytext margin-bottom-lg\">\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive table-responsive-all\">\r\n<table><colgroup> <col width=\"30\" /> <col width=\"633\" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" colspan=\"2\">GII THIU</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">\r\n<div>Chng trnh o to ti nng in t Vin thng c kim nh bi t chc kim nh quc t AUN-QA cung cp cho sinh vin cc kin thc vng chc trong lnh vc K thut in t Vin thng, Cng ngh thng tin.\r\nSinh vin chng trnh o to ti nng TVT c trang b mt cch ton din c v k nng chuyn mn v k nng mm  c th tr thnh nhng k s sng to, chuyn gia gii v nh lnh o trong:</div>\r\n<div>- Pht trin, thit k, ch to, vn hnh cc h thng in t thng minh nh thit k vi mch, h thng nhng, cc h thng in t ng dng trong truyn thng, y t, iu khin, t ng ha c hng ti cc ng dng thng minh nh hc my, tr tu nhn to.</div>\r\n<div>- Sng to cc nn tng phn cng, phn mm, cc phng thc truyn thng, h tng v ng dng cho mng Internet th h mi cng nh cc h thng x l thng tin hng ti nn cng nghip 5.0.</div>\r\n<div>c bit, sinh vin c khuyn khch thc tp trong mi trng doanh nghip sn xut sn phm, c tham gia nghin cu cng vi ging vin ti cc Vin Nghin cu v lnh vc in t, x l thng tin v truyn thng.</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" colspan=\"2\">CC CHUN U RA CA CHNG TRNH (PLO)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Sau khi tt nghip chng trnh ti nng in t - Vin thng, c nhn c cc kin thc, k nng v thi  nh sau:</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Pht trin cc h thng, thit b in t vin thng, CNTT  quy m nh bng cch p dng kin thc c s ton, vt l v c s ngnh.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Pht trin phn mm ng dng, firmware cho cc thit b v h thng in t, Vin thng, h thng x l tn hiu v thng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Sng to phn cng, mch in t, vi mch bn dn cho cc ng dng in t Vin thng, CNTT bng cch p dng cc kin thc chuyn ngnh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Xy dng quy trnh qun l, sn xut, kim tra thit b h thng TVT, CNTT</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">S dng thnh tho mt s ngn ng lp trnh c bn v nng cao  trin khai cc phn mm x l tn hiu, x l thng tin, iu khin trong cc thit b h thng in t vin thng, h thng cng ngh thng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">S dng thnh tho thit b o c, hn mch, s dng phn mm thit k</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">S dng ngoi ng ting Anh trong giao tip x hi v trong thc hnh chuyn mn cho cc k nng nghe ni c vit tng ngthp nht t mc TOEIC 600</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Th hin t duy phn bin, t duy sng to.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Th hin k nng trnh by, vit bo co, k nng lm vic c lp, lm vic nhm, k nng lnh o, k nng qun tr, qun l v kh nng hc tp sut i</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Th hin l ngi c  thc tn trng cc quy tc ngh nghip, tun th php lut.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" colspan=\"2\">NI DUNG &amp; L TRNH O TO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl71\" colspan=\"2\">Cu trc chng trnh o to ti nng ETTN gm cc khi kin thc c m t di y v l phin bn o to cht lng cao ca Khung chng trnh chun ET1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl72\">Khi kin thc i cng bao gm cc mn khoa hc t nhin v x hi c bn (Ton hc, Vt l, L lun chnh tr): y l khi kin thc mang li cho sinh vin t duy logic, sng to, phng php gii quyt vn  v hiu bit v lut php, t tng chnh tr.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl72\">Khi kin thc B tr: K nng mm, vn ha doanh nghip, t duy thit k, hc cch trnh by vn bn k thut v tt c cc cng c  bt k sinh vin no c th thch nghi c vi mi trng doanh nghip sau khi tt nghip</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl72\">Khi kin thc c s ngnh v ct li ngnh: Bao gm cc mn hc nn tng cho lnh vc in t vin thng nh Mch in t, x l tn hiu v thng tin, My tnh v lp trnh. Chng trnh ETTN  c nhng thay i v cp nht gip sinh vin c th tip cn vi kin thc ngnh sm hn v chuyn su hn so vi chng trnh chun ET1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl72\">Khi kin thc chuyn ngnh theo m un: Chng trnh ET1 c 6 modul chuyn ngnh t chn. Chng trnh ti nng TVT s tp trung vo nn tng ct li ca AIoT (Tr tu nhn to vn vt - Artificial Intelligence of Things) bao gm hp phn t chn v in t thng minh hoc v truyn thng thng minh cho cch mng cng nghip 5.0</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" colspan=\"2\">Chng trnh chi tit:</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl73\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl74\"><a href=\"https://qldt.hust.edu.vn/public#ctdt/code=ET-TN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">https://qldt.hust.edu.vn/public#ctdt/code=ET-TN</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'ET-TN-Chng trnh ti nng TVT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-13 02:39:11', '2025-05-13 02:39:11', '', 182, 'http://web-hust.test/?p=188', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
