EE-E18 (H thng in v Nng lng ti to).\r\n- 1  ti cp nh nc ang thc hin.\r\n-3  ticp nh nc  nghim thu\r\n-Xut bn 52gio trnh, s lng sch tham kho a dng v phong ph vi rt nhiu u sch.\r\n- Khong300 sinh vinnhp hc mi nm\r\n- 10 nhm chuyn mn:\r\n+ Nhm Li: Trng nhm TS. L Minh Khnh\r\n+ Nhm Nh my in: Trng nhm TS. Trng Ngc Minh\r\n+ Nhm Cung cp in: Trng nhm TS. L Vit Tin\r\n+ Nhm K thut in CA v Vt liu in: Trng nhm PGS. Trn Vn Tp\r\n+ Nhm Bo v v iu khin H thng in: Trng nhm TS. Nguyn Xun Tng\r\n+ Nhm Nng lng ti to: Trng nhm PGS. Nguyn c Huy\r\n+ Nhm K thut in: Trng nhm TS. Nguyn Nga Vit\r\n+ Nhm My in: Trng nhm PGS. Bi c Hng\r\n+ Nhm Thit b ng ct v bo v: TS. Phng Anh Tun\r\n+ Nhm Hiu qu nng lng: TS. Hong Anh\r\n- 3 phng LAB nghin cu:\r\n+ LAB HiPEMs (My in hiu nng cao) phng C7-E405.\r\n+ LAB H thng in v nng lng ti to, phng D9-300 v C1-112\r\n+ LAB H thng in thng minh, phng C1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl64\" colspan=\"2\">CHNG TRNH O TO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl66\" colspan=\"2\">Khoa in tp trung o to trong cc lnh vc Thit b in, C in cng trnh, H thng in, Nng lng ti to  tt c cc bc C nhn, Thc s, Tin s.\r\nNgnh K thut in xt tuyn sinh vi cc thng tin sau:\r\nM ngnh: EE1\r\n Xt tuyn ti nng: Xt tuyn bng Gii thng HSG QG-QT (din 1.1) /Chng ch Quc t (din 1.2)/HSNL &amp; phng vn (din 1.3)\r\n Xt tuyn theo kt qu k thi nh gi t duy (TSA)\r\n Xt tuyn theo kt qu k thi tt nghip THPT: A00, A01\r\n Ch tiu tuyn sinh: 240\r\n Ngn ng o to: Ting Vit\r\n Thi gian o to: 4 nm (C nhn) - 5.5 nm (Thc s) (S tn ch 132-180 tn ch)\r\n Hc ph: 24-30 triu ng/nm\r\nChng trnh o to ca ngnh K Thut in:\r\nc chia thnh 2 chng trnh:\r\n- Chng trnh tch hp c nhn  thc s (180 tn ch)\r\n- Chng trnh k s (180 tn ch)\r\nChng trnh o to K thut in ca i hc Bch khoa H Ni k tha truyn thng lch s v tip thu cc chng trnh o to tin tin t M, Chu u v Nht Bn, xy dng nn tng hc thut vng chc t c bn n cc ch  nng cao nh H thng in thng minh, Nng lng ti to v qun l d n nng lng. Sinh vin c trang b kin thc chuyn su v k nng thc hnh thng qua phng th nghim v thc tp cng nghip. nh hng ngh nghip bao gm thit k, vn hnh h thng in, nng lng ti to, t vn, v nghin cu pht trin trong lnh vc K thut in v nng lng.\r\nVi hai hng chuyn mn su l H thng in v Thit b in  in t, ngnh K thut in tp trung vo nghin cu v ng dng cc kin thc lin quan n lnh vc in, in t ng dng v in t trng vi nhiu khi kin thc lin quan nh C s in t tng t v s; H thng o v iu khin; X l tn hiu (AI, CNN); Kinh t nng lng; Thit k v bo tr my in (ng c in, my pht in); Thit k v ng dng cc thit b ng ct v bo v hin i; Nghin cu cc ngun nng lng ti to (nng lng gi, mt tri); Qun l v thit k h thng cung cp in v chiu sng (ta nh, nh my); Quy hoch v thit k h thng in; Phn tch v iu khin h thng in; Thit k, vn hnh cc Nh my in v trm bin p; T ng ha h thng in; Th trng in lc; Li in thng minh (Smart Grid, Micro Grid).....</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl66\" colspan=\"2\">Chng trnh tin tin H thng in v Nng lng ti to tuyn sinh vi cc thng tin nh sau:\r\n M ngnh: EE-E18\r\n Xt tuyn ti nng: Xt tuyn bng Gii thng HSG QG-QT (din 1.1) /Chng ch Quc t (din 1.2)/HSNL &amp; phng vn (din 1.3)\r\n Xt tuyn theo kt qu k thi nh gi t duy (TSA): K00\r\n Xt tuyn theo kt qu k thi tt nghip THPT: A00, A01\r\n Ch tiu tuyn sinh: 50\r\n Ngn ng o to: Ting Anh\r\n Thi gian o to: 4 nm (c nhn)  5,5 nm (Thc s) (S tn ch 132-180tn ch)\r\n Hc ph: 33-42 triu ng/nm\r\nChng trnh o to:\r\nChng trnh tin tin H thng in v Nng lng ti to thuc m ngnh K thut in ca i hc Bch khoa H Ni c xy dng da theo chng trnh o to ngnh K thut in, chuyn su h thng in v nng lng ti to ca cc trng i hc c v M. M ngnh EE-E18 c thc hin theo chng trnh tch hp c nhn  thc s (sau khi tt nghip c nhn vi 132 tn ch, sinh vin c th la chn hc ln thc s   180 tn ch). Mt s hc phn ca chng trnh o to s c ging dy bi cc gio s nc ngoi c uy tn. Sinh vin theo hc chng trnh tin tin H thng in v Nng lng ti to c nhiu li ch: c c hi c tham gia cc Lab nghin cu t sm; c hi nhn hc bng c gi tr t cc cng ty v doanh nghip; c c hi c tham gia cc chng trnh trao i sinh vin, thc tp k thut ti cc trng i hc v cng ty uy tn trong v ngoi nc. Sinh vin s c trang b nhng kin thc: L thuyt mch in  in t; H thng cung cp in; Quy hoch v thit k h thng in; Phn tch, bo v v iu khin h thng in; Thit k, vn hnh cc nh my in v trm bin p; T ng ha trong h thng in; Tch hp cc ngun nng lng ti to (nng lng gi, mt tri) vo h thng in;; Li in thng minh (Micro Grid, Smart Grid); Hiu qu nng lng; Khoa hc d liu ng dng trong nng lng..</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ElectricalEngineering.HUST\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/khoa-trung-tam/2024_10/dien-1.jpg\" alt=\"in 1\" width=\"1280\" height=\"800\" /></a><figcaption>Nhn</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/khoa-trung-tam/2024_10/dien-4.png\" alt=\"in 4\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" /><figcaption>Nhn</figcaption></figure>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/khoa-trung-tam/2024_10/dien-2.jpg\" alt=\"in 2\" width=\"1900\" height=\"1187\" /><figcaption>Nhn</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>', 'Gii thiu chung', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '300-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-13 14:41:59', '2025-05-13 14:41:59', '', 300, 'http://web-hust.test/?p=301', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
