  hp nht thnh Khoa K thut truyn thng vi tng s cn b l 43 cn b ging dy.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\" colspan=\"2\">CC CON S</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl66\" colspan=\"2\">Khoa K thut truyn thng c 43 Cn b ging dy, trong  c 1 GS, 15 PGS, 24 TS, 3 ThS</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl64\" colspan=\"2\">CHNG TRNH O TO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" colspan=\"2\">Khoa K thut truyn thng o to trong cc lnh vc K thut Truyn thng v K thut a phng tin  tt c cc bc C nhn, Thc s, Tin s.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Gii thiu chung', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gioi-thieu-chung-3', '', '', '2025-05-14 03:19:38', '2025-05-14 03:19:38', '', 0, 'http://web-hust.test/?post_type=center-department&#038;p=334', 0, 'center-department', '', 0),
