(342, 1, '2025-05-14 03:22:25', '2025-05-14 03:22:25', '<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"hometext m-bottom\">hoa in t, Trng in - in t l n v cp 3 thuc Trng i hc Bch khoa H Ni. Khoa c thnh lp ngy 18/11/2021 theo Quyt nh ca Hiu trng Trng i hc Bch khoa H Ni, trong l trnh ti chuyn i nh trng thnh m hnh i hc theo Lut Gio dc mi.\r\nKhoa in t l n v qun l chuyn mn ca 4 chng trnh o to c bit l : Chng trnh h thng nhng thng minh v IoT (ET-E9), Chng trnh ti nng in t vin thng (ET-TN), Chng trnh K thut y sinh (ET2), Chng trnh tin tin K thut y sinh (ET-E5)</div>\r\n<figure class=\"article center\"><img src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/khoa-trung-tam/2024_10/khoa-dt.jpg\" alt=\"Khoa T\" />\r\n<figcaption>Khoa T</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"news-bodyhtml\" class=\"bodytext margin-bottom-lg\">\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive table-responsive-all\">\r\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"102\" /><col width=\"633\" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" colspan=\"2\">GII THIU</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl66\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<div>Khoa in t, Trng in - in t l n v cp 3 thuc Trng i hc Bch khoa H Ni. Khoa c thnh lp ngy 18/11/2021 theo Quyt nh ca Hiu trng Trng i hc Bch khoa H Ni, trong l trnh ti chuyn i nh trng thnh m hnh i hc theo Lut Gio dc mi.\r\nKhoa in t l n v qun l chuyn mn ca 4 chng trnh o to c bit l : Chng trnh h thng nhng thng minh v IoT (ET-E9), Chng trnh ti nng in t vin thng (ET-TN), Chng trnh K thut y sinh (ET2), Chng trnh tin tin K thut y sinh (ET-E5). Khoa in t cng tham gia qun l chuyn mn chng trnh o to ngnh in t vin thng ET1  cc modul chuyn ngnh v K thut in t, k thut my tnh nhng, thit k vi mch v k thut y sinh. Ngoi ra Khoa in t cng qun l 11 nhm chuyn mn v k thut my tnh, mch v x l s tn hiu, cng ngh in t v k thut y sinh.\r\nTrit l gio dc ca Khoa in t nm trong trit l gio dc ca Trng in in t v i hc Bch Khoa H Ni  l \"ly ngi hc lm trung tm v hc phi i i vi thc hnh, theo ng nh hng cng ngh k thut hin i, o to k nng thc hnh v nghin cu p ng c nhu cu tuyn dng ca doanh nghip\".\r\nC cu t chc ca Khoa in t :\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ban Lnh o Khoa</li>\r\n 	<li> Cc trng nhm chuyn mn</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc gim c chng trnh o to</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc cn b ging dy</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr l khoa</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" colspan=\"2\">LCH S HNH THNH</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\" colspan=\"2\">Khoa in t tin thn l cc B mn in t v k thut my tnh, B mn Mch v x l tn hiu v B mn Cng ngh in t v K thut y sinh trc thuc qun l ca Khoa V tuyn ra i cng vi s thnh lp ca Trng HBK H Ni t nm 1956. n thng 18/11/2021 th 3 b mn  hp nht thnh Khoa in t vi tng s cn b l 35 cn b ging dy v 01 tr l khoa.\r\nTin thn ca B mn Mch v X l tn hiu l B mn C s v tuyn in c thnh lp vo nm 1957 do C Gio s Bi Minh Tiu lm Trng B mn. Lc , b mn c chia thnh ba nhm chuyn mn l nhm L thuyt mch, nhm K thut s v nhm K thut o lng. B mn gm 14 cn b ging dy v 5 cn b th nghim (khi  cha c ai c hc v Tin s v hc hm Ph Gio s, Gio s). B mn c 2 phng th nghim phc v cho ging dy v nghin cu khoa hc gm phng th nghim: mch v x l tin hiu v phng th nghim: o lng v truyn tin. Cc mn hc b mn ging dy gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cc mn c s ngnh cho sinh vin h i hc L thuyt mch; X l s tn hiu; Tn hiu v h thng; o lng; C s truyn tin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc mn: Project 1; Project 2; Project 3; Hng dn ATN; in t hc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc mn sau i hc X l tn hiu khng gian-thi gian; Truyn thng bng siu rng; X l nh s; Truyn thng a phng tin; Lc s v m ha bng con; M ha knh; Mng chuyn tip bng rng v ng dng; M hnh ha v m phng h thng; Ti u v tuyn cho cc mng thng tin di ng th h mi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nB mn K thut my tnh...\r\nB mn in t y sinh...</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl70\" colspan=\"2\">CC CON S</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl66\" colspan=\"2\">Khoa in t hin nay c tng s 35 Cn b, trong  c 08 PGS, 24 TS v 03 ThS.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" colspan=\"2\">CHNG TRNH O TO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\" colspan=\"2\">Khoa in t ph trch cc lnh vc chuyn mn o to v mch in t, x l tn hiu, in t tng t v in t s, h thng nhng v thit k IC, k thut lp trnh v phn mm, thit b v k thut y sinh.\r\n bc c nhn gm\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chng trnh T  VT chun (nh hng in t v k thut my tnh; K thut Y sinh)</li>\r\n 	<li>CTTT H thng nhng thng minh v IoT</li>\r\n 	<li>CTTT K thut Y sinh</li>\r\n 	<li>CT c nhn ti nng TVT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBc k s:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>K thut in t</li>\r\n 	<li>K thut Y sinh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBc thc s:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>K thut in t (chng trnh chun)</li>\r\n 	<li>K thut Y sinh (chng trnh chun)</li>\r\n 	<li>CTTT K thut in t</li>\r\n 	<li>CTTT K thut Y sinh</li>\r\n 	<li>CTTT in t - H thng nhng thng minh</li>\r\n 	<li>CT ti nng in t vin thng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBc Tin s:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>K thut in t (chng trnh chun)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Gii thiu chung', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gioi-thieu-chung-4', '', '', '2025-05-14 03:22:25', '2025-05-14 03:22:25', '', 0, 'http://web-hust.test/?post_type=center-department&#038;p=342', 0, 'center-department', '', 0),
