(517, 1, '2025-05-15 06:45:09', '2025-05-15 06:45:09', 'Trng in  in t l n v cp 2 thuc HBKHN v l n v o to v nghin cu nngct trong lnh vc in  in t, c tnh t ch cao thuc HBKHN, c chc nng chnh l oto cp bng, NCKH v chuyn giao tri thc trong lnh vc chuyn mn in  in t, k thuta phng tin\r\n\r\n<strong>Mc tiu chin lc ca Trng in  in t l thnh</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>n v o to ngun nhn lc trnh  cao cho ngnh in, T-VT vi nh hng tchhp, lin ngnh in, T-VT, p ng cc yu cu nhn lc x hi cng nh ca th trnglao ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>n v nghin cu, pht trin v ng dng cng ngh lin ngnh in, T-VT c uy tn trong nc cng nh khu vc v th gii;</li>\r\n 	<li>a ch u t, hp tc v CGCN hp dn, tin cy i vi cc t chc, cc doanh nghiptrong nc v quc t;</li>\r\n 	<li>n v ng vai tr quan trng vo qu trnh pht trin ngnh in, T-VT Vit Nam,gp phn quan trng trong s nghip pht trin kinh t - x hi, CNH &amp; HH t nc,gi gn an ninh, quc phng.</li>\r\n 	<li>L mt trong cc n v i u, ng gp tch cc vo s pht trin chung theo chin lcpht trin ca HBKHN.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Mc tiu n nm 2030</strong>\r\n\r\nCc mc tiu pht trin 2021  2025 s l c s  5 nm tip theo (2025  2030), aTrngin  in t ln mt bc pht trin mi vi cc mc tiu c bn nh sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tip tc gi vng v th s mt Vit Nam v o to trong lnh vc in  in t.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr thnh mt c s o to c uy tn  ng Nam  trong lnh vc in  in t, cnhiu i tc bit n v c hp tc quc t su rng trong lnh vc NCKH, trao i sinh vin, ging vin. Tng bc tng s lng sinh vin quc t.</li>\r\n 	<li>L c s o to i hc, sau i hc hin i, hi nhp quc t th hin qua: s lngchng trnh ging dy bng ting Anh; phng php ging dy hin i, s dng c sh tng s; cc chng trnh o to c kim nh quc t; cht lng c nhn/k s/thcs/tin s ra trng c cc n v s dng nh gi cao; t l s hc vin cao hc/NCStrn sinh vin i hc tng ng k so vi hin nay.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Gii thiu chung', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gioi-thieu-chung', '', '', '2025-06-16 10:48:12', '2025-06-16 03:48:12', '', 0, 'http://web-hust.test/?post_type=introduction&#038;p=517', 0, 'introduction', '', 0),
