(1105, 1, '2025-06-12 15:14:11', '2025-06-12 08:14:11', '<div class=\"clearfix\">\n<div class=\"hometext m-bottom\">\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\n<div class=\"hometext m-bottom\">Vi hai hng chuyn mn su l H thng in v Thit b in  in t, ngnh K thut in tp trung vo nghin cu v ng dng cc kin thc lin quan n lnh vc in, in t ng dng v in t trng vi nhiu khi kin thc lin quan</div>\n<figure class=\"article center\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail\" src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/dao-tao/2024_10/ee1-new.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/seee/mobile/dao-tao/2024_10/ee1-new.jpg 480w, /uploads/seee/dao-tao/2024_10/ee1-new.jpg 1200w\" alt=\"EE1\" width=\"460\" /><figcaption>EE1</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div id=\"news-bodyhtml\" class=\"bodytext margin-bottom-lg\">\n\n<strong>Ngnh K thut in xt tuyn sinh vi cc thng tin sau:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>M ngnh: EE1</li>\n 	<li>Xt tuyn ti nng, Xt tuyn bng Gii thng HSG QG-QT (din 1.1) /Chng ch Quc t (din 1.2)/HSNL &amp; phng vn (din 1.3)</li>\n 	<li>Xt tuyn theo kt qu k thi nh gi t duy (TSA)</li>\n 	<li>Xt tuyn theo kt qu k thi tt nghip THPT: A00, A01</li>\n 	<li>Ch tiu tuyn sinh: 240</li>\n 	<li>Ngn ng o to: Ting Vit</li>\n 	<li>Thi gian o to: 4 nm (C nhn)  5,5 nm (Thc s) (S tn ch 132-180 tn ch); o to k s bc 7 - 5,5 nm</li>\n 	<li>Hc ph: 24-30 triu ng/nm</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Chng trnh o to ca ngnh K Thut in</strong>\nc chia thnh 2 chng trnh:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Chng trnh tch hp c nhn  thc s (180 tn ch)</li>\n 	<li>Chng trnh k s (180 tn ch)</li>\n</ul>\nVi hai hng chuyn mn su l H thng in v Thit b in  in t, ngnh K thut in tp trung vo nghin cu v ng dng cc kin thc lin quan n lnh vc in, in t ng dng v in t trng vi nhiu khi kin thc lin quan nh C s in t tng t v s; H thng o v iu khin; X l tn hiu (AI, CNN); Kinh t nng lng; Thit k v bo tr my in (ng c in, my pht in); Thit k v bo tr cc thit b ng ct v bo v hin i; Nghin cu cc ngun nng lng ti to (nng lng gi, mt tri); Qun l v thit k h thng cung cp in v chiu sng (ta nh, nh my); Quy hoch v thit k h thng in; Phn tch v iu khin h thng in; Thit k, vn hnh cc Nh my in v trm bin p; T ng ha h thng in; Th trng in lc; Li in thng minh (Smart Grid, Micro Grid).....\n\n<strong>Hc bng</strong>\n\nSinh vin c nhiu c hi nhn hc bng trong khi hc C nhn ca Trng HBK, hc bng t cc cng ty, tp on trong v ngoi nc EVN, kinh ph h tr khi thc tp ti cc tp on EVN, OWC (Anh), EDF (Php) , Toshiba (Nht Bn), hc bng trao i sinh vin ti nc ngoi theo cc chng trnh: Shibaura, Doshisha, AUN/SEED-Net, i Loan, cc Lab c hp tc vi khoa in... Sau khi tt nghip, c c hi hc nhn hc bng tip tc hc cc bc cao hn nh Thc s v Tin s trong nc v nc ngoi ti chu u, c, M, Canada, Nht Bn, i Loan, Hn Quc theo cc hc bng chnh ph v Lab nghin cu c mi quan h vi Khoa in.\n\n<strong>K nng t c sau khi tt nghip ngnh K Thut in:</strong>\nVi cc kin thc c trang b trong qu trnh o to, khi tt nghip ngnh K thut in, sinh vin c kh nng thc hin cc cng vic sau:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Tnh ton, iu khin h thng in quc gia, cc min, vn hnh th trng in;</li>\n 	<li>T vn, thit k li in, nh my in v trm bin p; cc h thng nng lng ti to;</li>\n 	<li>Qun l, vn hnh, bo dng li in, nh my in v trm bin p;</li>\n 	<li>Thit k, qun l, vn hnh h thng in v chiu sng trong cc cao c, nh my cng nghip, sn vn ng hng n cc cng trnh xanh (net-zero);</li>\n 	<li>Qun l, gim st cc d n k thut, kim ton nng lng;</li>\n 	<li>Thi cng, xy lp cc cng trnh in lc (h p, trung p v cao p);</li>\n 	<li>Nghin cu v pht trin cc ng c in cho dn dng, cng nghip v giao thng vn ti, my pht in mt pha - ba pha cho dn dng, cng nghip v nng lng ti to, thit b ng ct v bo v hin i;</li>\n 	<li>Bo tr, bo dng v nh gi tui th ca thit b in;</li>\n 	<li>Nghin cu, pht trin cc thit b t ng thng minh v h thng gim st, iu khin hin i.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Cc v tr vic lm tiu biu sau khi tt nghip ngnh K thut in:</strong>\n\nTt nghip ngnh K thut in, sinh vin c kh nng lm vic ti cc v tr vic lm tiu biu nh sau:\n<ul>\n 	<li>K s nghin cu, thit k, vn hnh ti cc tp on c vn u t nc ngoi (FDI) trong lnh vc Thit b in v H thng in;</li>\n 	<li>K s thit k ti cc cng ty t vn thit k i