(1112, 1, '2025-06-12 15:14:16', '2025-06-12 08:14:16', '<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"hometext m-bottom\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"hometext m-bottom\">Vi hai hng chuyn mn su l H thng in v Thit b in  in t, ngnh K thut in tp trung vo nghin cu v ng dng cc kin thc lin quan n lnh vc in, in t ng dng v in t trng vi nhiu khi kin thc lin quan</div>\r\n<figure class=\"article center\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail\" src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/dao-tao/2024_10/ee1-new.jpg\" srcset=\"/assets/seee/mobile/dao-tao/2024_10/ee1-new.jpg 480w, /uploads/seee/dao-tao/2024_10/ee1-new.jpg 1200w\" alt=\"EE1\" width=\"460\" /><figcaption>EE1</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"news-bodyhtml\" class=\"bodytext margin-bottom-lg\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Ngnh K thut in xt tuyn sinh vi cc thng tin sau:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>M ngnh: EE1</li>\r\n 	<li>Xt tuyn ti nng, Xt tuyn bng Gii thng HSG QG-QT (din 1.1) /Chng ch Quc t (din 1.2)/HSNL &amp; phng vn (din 1.3)</li>\r\n 	<li>Xt tuyn theo kt qu k thi nh gi t duy (TSA)</li>\r\n 	<li>Xt tuyn theo kt qu k thi tt nghip THPT: A00, A01</li>\r\n 	<li>Ch tiu tuyn sinh: 240</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngn ng o to: Ting Vit</li>\r\n 	<li>Thi gian o to: 4 nm (C nhn)  5,5 nm (Thc s) (S tn ch 132-180 tn ch); o to k s bc 7 - 5,5 nm</li>\r\n 	<li>Hc ph: 24-30 triu ng/nm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Chng trnh o to ca ngnh K Thut in</strong>\r\nc chia thnh 2 chng trnh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chng trnh tch hp c nhn  thc s (180 tn ch)</li>\r\n 	<li>Chng trnh k s (180 tn ch)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nVi hai hng chuyn mn su l H thng in v Thit b in  in t, ngnh K thut in tp trung vo nghin cu v ng dng cc kin thc lin quan n lnh vc in, in t ng dng v in t trng vi nhiu khi kin thc lin quan nh C s in t tng t v s; H thng o v iu khin; X l tn hiu (AI, CNN); Kinh t nng lng; Thit k v bo tr my in (ng c in, my pht in); Thit k v bo tr cc thit b ng ct v bo v hin i; Nghin cu cc ngun nng lng ti to (nng lng gi, mt tri); Qun l v thit k h thng cung cp in v chiu sng (ta nh, nh my); Quy hoch v thit k h thng in; Phn tch v iu khin h thng in; Thit k, vn hnh cc Nh my in v trm bin p; T ng ha h thng in; Th trng in lc; Li in thng minh (Smart Grid, Micro Grid).....\r\n\r\n<strong>Hc bng</strong>\r\n\r\nSinh vin c nhiu c hi nhn hc bng trong khi hc C nhn ca Trng HBK, hc bng t cc cng ty, tp on trong v ngoi nc EVN, kinh ph h tr khi thc tp ti cc tp on EVN, OWC (Anh), EDF (Php) , Toshiba (Nht Bn), hc bng trao i sinh vin ti nc ngoi theo cc chng trnh: Shibaura, Doshisha, AUN/SEED-Net, i Loan, cc Lab c hp tc vi khoa in... Sau khi tt nghip, c c hi hc nhn hc bng tip tc hc cc bc cao hn nh Thc s v Tin s trong nc v nc ngoi ti chu u, c, M, Canada, Nht Bn, i Loan, Hn Quc theo cc hc bng chnh ph v Lab nghin cu c mi quan h vi Khoa in.\r\n\r\n<strong>K nng t c sau khi tt nghip ngnh K Thut in:</strong>\r\nVi cc kin thc c trang b trong qu trnh o to, khi tt nghip ngnh K thut in, sinh vin c kh nng thc hin cc cng vic sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tnh ton, iu khin h thng in quc gia, cc min, vn hnh th trng in;</li>\r\n 	<li>T vn, thit k li in, nh my in v trm bin p; cc h thng nng lng ti to;</li>\r\n 	<li>Qun l, vn hnh, bo dng li in, nh my in v trm bin p;</li>\r\n 	<li>Thit k, qun l, vn hnh h thng in v chiu sng trong cc cao c, nh my cng nghip, sn vn ng hng n cc cng trnh xanh (net-zero);</li>\r\n 	<li>Qun l, gim st cc d n k thut, kim ton nng lng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Thi cng, xy lp cc cng trnh in lc (h p, trung p v cao p);</li>\r\n 	<li>Nghin cu v pht trin cc ng c in cho dn dng, cng nghip v giao thng vn ti, my pht in mt pha - ba pha cho dn dng, cng nghip v nng lng ti to, thit b ng ct v bo v hin i;</li>\r\n 	<li>Bo tr, bo dng v nh gi tui th ca thit b in;</li>\r\n 	<li>Nghin cu, pht trin cc thit b t ng thng minh v h thng gim st, iu khin hin i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Cc v tr vic lm tiu biu sau khi tt nghip ngnh K thut in:</strong>\r\n\r\nTt nghip ngnh K thut in, sinh vin c kh nng lm vic ti cc v tr vic lm tiu biu nh sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>K s nghin cu, thit k, vn hnh ti cc tp on c vn u t nc ngoi (FDI) trong lnh vc Thit b in v H thng in;</li>\r\n 	<li>K s thit k ti cc cng ty t vn thit k in, thit b in, xy lp my, xy lp in, cc nh my nhit in, thy in, in gi, in mt tri; cc doanh nghip nh nc ph trch quy chun an ton in thuc B cng thng, B xy dng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc cng ty thit k, nghin cu v sn xut thit b in - in t, cc thit b in thng minh v.v...;</li>\r\n 	<li>Cn b nghin cu, ging dy ti cc trng i hc, cc vin nghin cu</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Ph trch t vn chuyn su v CTT:</strong>\r\nEE1  K thut in\r\nGim c CTT: TS. Nguyn Nga Vit\r\nEmail: viet.nguyennga@hust.edu.vn\r\nin thoi: 0333 439 321\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>File nh km</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"news-bodyhtml\" class=\"bodytext margin-bottom-lg\">\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive table-responsive-all\">\r\n<div class=\"list-group news-download-file\">\r\n<div class=\"list-group-item\"><i class=\"fa fa-eye\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"tooltip\" data-content=\"Xem trc\" data-original-title=\"\"></i><a title=\"Tp tin thong-bao-so-1-hnkhkttq-viii-giap-lai.pdf\" href=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/vi/news/hoat-dong-chung/hoi-nghi-khoa-hoc-ky-thuat-do-luong-toan-quoc-lan-thu-viii-317650.html?download=1&amp;id=0\" download=\"\">Tp tin : </a><a href=\"http://web-hust.test/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ctdt-dien-1-ee1-program-final.137618.10284.pdf\">ctdt-dien-1-ee1-program-final.137618.10284</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'EE1-K thut in', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '184-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-06-12 15:14:16', '2025-06-12 08:14:16', '', 184, 'http://web-hust.test/?p=1112', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1113, 1, '2025-06-12 15:16:16', '2025-06-12 08:16:16', '<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"hometext m-bottom\">Truyn thng s v k thut a phng tin l ngnh nghin cu v ng dng cc k thut thu thp, x l, to ni dung v truyn thng d liu/ thng tin s a phng tin nh vn bn,  ha, hnh nh, m thanh, hot ha, hot hnh, video. y l cu ni quan trng gia cng ngh thng tin v in t nhm to ra cc sn phm p ng yu cu trng tm ca cuc cch mng cng nghip 4.0.</div>\r\n<figure class=\"article center\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail\" src=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/uploads/seee/dao-tao/2024_09/et-e16-anh-dao-tao.png\" srcset=\"/assets/seee/mobile/dao-tao/2024_09/et-e16-anh-dao-tao.png 480w, /uploads/seee/dao-tao/2024_09/et-e16-anh-dao-tao.png 711w\" alt=\"ET E16 Anh Dao tao\" width=\"460\" /><figcaption>ET E16 Anh Dao tao</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"news-bodyhtml\" class=\"bodytext margin-bottom-lg\">\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive table-responsive-all\">\r\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"30\" /><col width=\"633\" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl71\" colspan=\"2\">GII THIU</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl66\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Truyn thng s v k thut a phng tin l ngnh nghin cu v ng dng cc k thut thu thp, x l, to ni dung v truyn thng d liu/ thng tin s a phng tin nh vn bn,  ha, hnh nh, m thanh, hot ha, hot hnh, video. y l cu ni quan trng gia cng ngh thng tin v in t nhm to ra cc sn phm p ng yu cu trng tm ca cuc cch mng cng nghip 4.0.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl71\" colspan=\"2\">CC CHUN U RA CA CHNG TRNH (PLO)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Sau khi tt nghip chng trnh truyn thng s v K thut a phng tin, c nhn c cc kin thc, k nng v thi  nh sau:</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">C kin thc ton v khoa hc c bn, c s ngnh, v chuyn ngnh v K thut truyn thng s (gm cc h thng phn cng phn mm thu thp, x l tnh ton v truyn thng d liu a phng tin, mng truyn thng v k thut truyn hnh) v a phng tin (x l, biu din, lu tr v tm kim d liu d liu hnh nh, m thanh, vn bn,  ha da trn cc k thut x l tn hiu, tr tu nhn to, hc my; to ni dung s a phng tin, web, game, ng dng di ng c tnh n yu t tri nghim ngi dng) vng chc  m bo kh nng t o to nng cao trnh  chuyn mn.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">M hnh ha v phng to h thng truyn thng s v x l d liu a phng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Thit k m hnh truyn thng s v a phng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Thit k v pht trin h thng x l v sng to ni dung s a phng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">S dng thnh tho mt s cng c nn tng trong lnh vc truyn thng s v k thut a phng tin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">S dng thnh tho mt s ngn ng lp trnh c bn v nng cao</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">S dng ngoi ng trong giao tip x hi v thc hnh chuyn mn (IELTS 5.5 hoc tng ng)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Th hin k nng qun tr, qun l v hc tp sut i</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Thnh tho k nng trnh by, vit bo co</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Th hin k nng lm vic c lp v lm vic nhm</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Th hin t duy phn bin v sng to ni dung s</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\">Tun th php lut v tn trng quy tc ngh nghip</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl71\" colspan=\"2\">NI DUNG &amp; L TRNH O TO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl72\" colspan=\"2\">Chng trnh o to Truyn thng s v k thut a phng tin bao gm cc khi kin thc chnh:</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Khi kin thc i cngbao gm cc mn khoa hc t nhin v x hi c bn (Ton hc, Vt l, L lun chnh tr)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Thu thp v truyn thng d liu s PT(H iu hnh, Vi x l, Kin trc my tnh , in t s, Thng tin s, Mng my tnh, K thut truyn hnh, Internet th h mi, in ton m my/bin)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Qun l v x l d liu s PT(C s d liu, Cu trc d liu &amp; gii thut, Phn tch v trc quan ho d liu; X l tn hiu s, Nn v m ho d liu, X l tn hiu m thanh, X l nh, X l ngn ng t nhin)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Phn tch hiu ni dung s PT s dng AI(Hc my c bn, Hc my nng cao, Th gic my tnh, Nhn dng v tng hp ting ni)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"xl68\"></td>\r\n<td class=\"xl69\">Sn xut ni dung v trin khai d n PT( ho my tnh, Lp trnh game, Lp trnh web v di ng, K xo in nh, Sn xut ni dung s a phng tin, , Lp trnh C/C++, Lp trnh nng cao, Phn tch thit k h thng, Tng tc ngi my, Qun l d n)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'ET-E16-Truyn thng s v K thut a phng tin', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-06-12 15:16:16', '2025-06-12 08:16:16', '', 182, 'http://web-hust.test/?p=1113', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
